# Working artifacts — stay LOCAL; never ship to public surface.
# Policy invariant: the developer keeps ALL working files local; the GitHub repo
# is a clean installable public release. Every local-only working surface (plans,
# audits, handoffs, ADRs, roadmap, research, recovery, vision, agent CHANGELOGs,
# BACKLOG, ledger, persona sources) now lives under a single .development/ tree —
# one ignore rule, enforced by the CI leak-guard (.github/workflows/leak-guard.yml).
.development/
*:Zone.Identifier
